<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA53">
<l>ceṉṟāṟ kuṭaiyā miruntāṟciṅ kācaṉamā</l>
<l>niṉṟāṉ maravaṭiyā nīḷkaṭaluḷ – ḷeṉṟum</l>
<l>puṇaiyā maṇiviḷakkām pūmpaṭṭām pulku</l>
<l>maṇaiyān, tirumāṟ karavu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When He goes it is [his] parasol, when He sits it is [his] lion throne,</l>
<l>when He stands it is [his] sandals, in the large ocean always</l>
<l>it is [his] raft, [his] jewel lamp is it, [and his] beautiful silk garment, the bed</l>
<l>where He embraces [Śrī] is Tirumāl’s serpent.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
